    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "The Protest Before Christmas",
        "Description": "Santa Klaus has been a naughty boy. With his rise to stardom, he&apos;s shifted to strict elf labour with increased hours and decreased pay. The elves have plotted to kill him, but Santa found out. He and 4 of his fellow old people are hiding in Paris, but it&apos;s a good thing one certain elf is a proud protester...\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Amiithyst.",
